======================================================================
  PART 2: THE FIBONACCI ↔ x=11 BRIDGE
======================================================================

Fibonacci (x=1): f(n) = f(n-1) + f(n-2)
  Roots: φ = (1+√5)/2 ≈ 1.618, ψ = (1-√5)/2 ≈ -0.618
  F(n) = (φⁿ - ψⁿ)/√5

x=11 recurrence: f(n) = f(n-1) + 11·f(n-2)
  Roots: (1+3√5)/2 = 3φ-1 ≈ 3.854, (1-3√5)/2 = -3/φ ≈ -2.854
  G(n) = ((3φ-1)ⁿ - (-(3/φ))ⁿ) / (3√5)

  3φ - 1 = 3.8541019662
  (1+3√5)/2 = 3.8541019662
  Match: True

  n   Fib(n)     G₁₁(n)    G₁₁/Fib     G₁₁ mod 5
