  13       233     6295873  27020.9142      3
  14       377    23431057  62151.3448      2
  15       610    92685660  151943.7049      0

G₁₁(n) mod 5: [1, 1, 2, 3, 0, 3, 3, 1, 4, 0, 4, 4, 3, 2, 0]
Fib(n) mod 5: [1, 1, 2, 3, 0, 3, 3, 1, 4, 0, 4, 4, 3, 2, 0]

Asymptotic ratio G₁₁(n)/F(n) → ((3φ-1)/φ)ⁿ / 3
  (3φ-1)/φ = 3 - 1/φ = 2.3819660113
  = (7-√5)/2 = 2.3819660113


