======================================================================
  PART 6: (3,5)-PACKING AT n=8
======================================================================

At n=8 = 2³, the first cross-level (3,5) packing appears.
A disjoint (3-cycle, 5-cycle) pair uses 3+5=8 = ALL vertices.
So at n=8, a (3,5) pair is a PARTITION of the vertex set.

